(958, 2000000043, 'evOps not only offers better organisational support for software maintenance but also enhances communication between developers and operations teams, leading to more effective maintenance strategies.\n*   A fundamental principle of DevOps is the \"you build it, you own it\" philosophy, which asserts that the developers who create code are also responsible for its deployment and ongoing maintenance. Even if the organisation doesn’t fully embrace this principle, it likely fosters increased collaboration between developers and IT operations. Consequently, when production issues arise or upgrades are necessary for maintaining reliability, developers are actively involved in resolving these matters.\n    *   Source: [https://devops.com/making-software-maintenance-cool-devops/](https://devops.com/making-software-maintenance-cool-devops/)\n\n#### 1.9.1 DevOps and Maintenance', '[0.018233847,-0.006543404,-0.012358845,0.021242853,-0.051348567,0.01918359,0.004929688,0.06355147,-0.020604303,-0.015340157,-0.013552978,0.026594961,0.07485134,-0.0007067046,0.048973497,-0.05886635,0.025049806,0.055566736,-0.062401287,0.0096820425,0.011826759,-0.004581447,-0.057061356,-0.046346225,-0.0014767293,-0.048176058,0.07718473,0.011875619,-0.023287887,-0.0479428,-0.013785092,0.029139163,-0.0028354123,-0.033517648,-0.040981885,-0.006534877,0.013745141,0.008108102,-0.038600933,0.0028369967,-0.020401014,-0.062796324,-0.06125057,0.04391005,0.02481071,0.046716608,-0.013068752,0.02480782,0.034198422,0.037883457,0.023485977,-0.016785989,-0.027224189,0.03140094,-0.003130365,-0.030238837,-0.040270098,-0.00042248267,0.041463874,-0.014972016,-0.041898295,-0.01682891,-0.01945033,-0.03655997,0.021855503,0.036098324,-0.043327834,-0.061746847,-0.05815453,-0.004518009,-0.020472525,0.017238466,-0.05046135,0.023983086,0.0016762308,-0.0019870852,-0.0009541841,-0.06701715,-0.01014144,0.022222392,0.03940244,-0.018540828,0.10761365,-0.021641051,-0.0053888042,-0.047862325,-0.04192124,-0.0457483,