(974, 2000000044, 'production environments in a new Region or virtual private cloud (VPC) in minutes.\n*   **OpsWorks:** Manage and deploy applications across fleets.\n\n### Key Takeaways: AWS Disaster Recovery Planning\n\n*   Use features such as CRR (Cross-Region Replication), EBS volume snapshots, and Amazon RDS snapshots to protect data.\n*   Use networking features, such as Route 53 failover and ELB, to improve application availability.\n*   Use automation services, such as CloudFormation, as part of your DR strategy to quickly deploy duplicate environments when needed.\n*   Use EventBridge to use global endpoints to automatically restore data and failover to functioning servers.\n\n## 8. Disaster Recovery Patterns\n\n### Common Disaster Recovery Patterns on AWS\n\nEach pattern is suited to a different combination of RPO, RTO, and cost-effectiveness.\n\n*   Backup and restore\n*   Pilot light\n*   Warm standby\n*   Multi-site\n\n### Backup and Restore Pattern', '[0.027434358,-0.039450668,-0.05349843,0.015488691,0.02334866,0.014413006,0.031299286,-0.011101139,-0.022846187,0.0007272925,-0.007313235,0.025617352,-0.022952653,0.026620906,0.018918527,-0.060638517,0.105534665,0.029399194,-0.032849867,0.011869405,0.034104135,0.024502505,0.013882739,-0.075159945,-0.042016268,-0.0048176437,0.0044998834,-0.025306754,-0.012849595,-0.007392051,0.0065802177,0.029682757,0.063014984,-0.01298982,0.019999888,-0.014589617,0.010320836,-0.021631181,0.030283218,-0.016951244,-0.06392793,0.011877515,-0.03713087,0.06648992,-0.016706426,0.007661178,-0.08012779,0.08283701,-0.04259276,-0.019170655,0.020086091,0.021751836,-0.02950588,0.024785897,0.03205753,-0.050952304,-0.036674727,-0.03642421,-0.004292255,0.029602189,-0.055357017,-0.0052765496,0.0026562684,0.023656325,0.06596799,-0.015580002,-0.044660687,0.009311933,-0.035906713,0.052752692,0.019387467,0.05573806,0.034642868,0.031466465,-0.019017607,-0.001114527,0.03123845,0.0075523583,-0.044885743,0.043905105,0.022866948,0.0053427923,0.1